titles.title: A bill to extend the temporary suspension of duty on 1-{1-((4-Chloro-2-(trifluoromethyl)-penyl)imino)-2-propoxymethyl}-1-H-imidazole, and for other purposes.

action.text: Sponsor introductory remarks on measure. (CR S4772-4774)
Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 4/21/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 1998, the duty on 1(1-((4-chloro-2-(trifluoromethyl)phenyl)imino)-2- propoxyethyl)-1-H-imidazole.
